snippet: Alex Ovechkin returned from a shoulder injury to score his 11th and 12th goals of the season as the Washington Capitals defeated the visiting Islanders, 6-2.
abstract: Washington Capitals beat New York Islanders, 6-2; other hockey news noted.
lead_paragraph: Alex Ovechkin returned from a shoulder injury to score his 11th and 12th goals of the season as the Washington Capitals defeated the visiting Islanders, 6-2.
